## When Updating the App
- Use `sq agent-tools query-expert execute-query` to pull fresh data from Snowflake
- Use the query in `sql/09_full_leaderboard_corrected.sql` as the canonical source
- After updating app/index.html, push to GitHub: `cd /Users/nateobermark/rev-up-contest && git add -A && git commit -m "..." && git push`
- The GitHub Pages site auto-deploys from main branch
